      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is just so quiet now. i keep looking at the corner where his bed used to be and it just feels like there's nothing left. i'm so tired of carrying this heaviness. it's like i'm just moving through sludge every day. i don't even know why i'm bothering to get up anymore.",
