      "content": "i hear you, but it doesn't feel like it's going to get manageable. it just feels endless. like i'm just waiting for something to change but nothing ever does. sometimes i look at the silence in this house and i just think... what's even the point of fighting it? i just want the weight to stop. i want everything to just be still.",
